Package com.example.nachos_app

Class Event

java.lang.Object
com.example.nachos_app.Event
public class Event extends Object
Model class representing an event in the lottery system. This class stores all event-related information including registration periods, participant limits, and QR code data.

    • Event

      public Event(String organizerId, String organizerName, String eventName, String description, String registrationRange, Date registrationStartDate, Date registrationEndDate, Date eventDate, Integer maxParticipants, String bannerUrl, String qrCodeUrl, String qrCodeData, Date createdAt, String eventLocation)
      Constructs a new Event with all required fields.
      Parameters:
      organizerId - ID of the user who created the event
      organizerName - name of the organizer
      eventName - name/title of the event
      description - description of the event
      registrationRange - registration range
      registrationStartDate - registration opens
      registrationEndDate - registration closes
      eventDate - date when the event occurs (can be null)
      maxParticipants - Maximum waitlist capacity (null for unlimited)
      bannerUrl - Base64 encoded event poster image
      qrCodeUrl - Base64 encoded QR code image
      qrCodeData - The data encoded in the QR code (event:// URL)
      createdAt - Timestamp when the event was created
      eventLocation - optional event's location
